{"tid":1779592,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"急問下咩地方買到呢樽眼藥水","createTime":"2019-12-11T19:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T23:34:39.000Z","uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f42c28638da9c12b0bf89ea9c268d0995ace1c00","tid":1779592,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:04:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n背景:80+老人家<br />\n幾年前做了青光眼手術，醫生要佢長滴博士倫博舒坦眼用液劑(bausch and lomb latanoprost ophthalmic solution)，<br />\n滴宂一樽就番去橡查，老人家長居大陸，唔肯次次滴完就番黎香港睇，家人香港買藥水俾佢就肯滴，<br />\n老人家3~4個月先番黎見醫生一次。篱生知佢自己買藥，由得佢，但又唔會開多兩樽俾佢。<br />\n一向家人都買到藥水，但呢排買唔到(以前長沙灣藥房買)，<br />\n想問下咁多巴絲，知唔知咩地方買到?謝<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAqYpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAqYpf.jpg&h=694ad6b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9005183e561186f76bb59e6d302098fd211721e6","tid":1779592,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T23:34:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇巴絲幫到?</span>"}]}